            <title>雷鸟推出“青鸟”系列真壁纸电视：4K 144Hz 高刷，4199 元起</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/768/996.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/768/996.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Sat, 18 May 2024 13:59:43 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1790356" rel="nofollow">很宅很怕生</a> 的线索投递！</div>
